      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"journey\" stuff feels so hollow right now. It's not about finding new spots on a map. It’s more like... when you reach the edge of the world, you just stop. There's no point in walking in circles once you know how the story ends. I just feel like I've completed my itinerary and there's nothing left to check off. Everything feels very heavy and very final.",
